  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Guided walking holidays in Europe</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13108627/adobestock_269044912-1.jpg" alt="guided walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/237ece5d16ea4959b9809ac3b4f49f9f" /></p>
<h3>Our Guided Walks</h3>
<p>As part of your holiday, many of our resorts offer the chance to join up to two exclusive guided day walks, led by an experienced local guide.</p>
<p>Choose from one easy-to-moderate walk and one more challenging option each week - or take on both! Starting and ending in your resort, there’s no need for heavy packs or overnight stays, and you'll be back in time for dinner.</p>
<p>With limited spaces, we recommend reserving your spot when you book, <span>or add one onto your holiday through 'Manage My Booking.'</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>✔️ Up to two walks per week with a professional walking guide</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>✔️ Expert advice and recommended walks from your representative</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>✔️ Professional recommendations on things to do in resort</strong></p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Walk with us</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Experience the great outdoors with our passionate guides, bringing nature and local culture to life. Visit our <a data-udi="umb://document/0a9463ae3330459497529444caf4782c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0a9463ae3330459497529444caf4782c}" title="Grades">Graded Walking page</a> for walks tailored to your level - easy, challenging, or somewhere in between and explore our top destination recommendations.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="#austria" data-anchor="#austria">Austria</a> | <a href="#france" data-anchor="#france">France</a> | <a href="#italy" data-anchor="#italy">Italy</a> | <a href="#madeira" data-anchor="#madeira">Madeira</a> | <a href="#slovenia" data-anchor="#slovenia">Slovenia</a> | <a href="#switzerland" data-anchor="#switzerland">Switzerland</a></p>
<h3 id="austria" style="text-align: left;">Austria Guided Walks</h3>
<div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102797/ahorn-mayrhofen_adobestock_88734716.jpg" alt="Mayrhofen guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/132c50455d0040e290dd23c7b1620f8e" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><strong>Two full day guided walks a week from a program of eight walks.</strong></p>
<p>Prepare to be amazed at every turn by the diverse walking options around Mayrhofen, featuring hundreds of trails and incredible mountain views.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13107088/seefeld-2.jpg" alt="seefeld" data-udi="umb://media/0673a31b175c4f84983e91bc92255c4e" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a></h4>
<p><strong>A full day guided walk every Monday and Thursday.</strong>    </p>
<p><span>Immerse yourself in stunning panoramic views throughout this remarkable walking region, as you venture along beautiful trails through Tirol’s Hochplateau.</span></p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13107089/adobestock_218668684-1.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/5659d7bcd431429d92efc57d3425675b" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b}" title="Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm">Saalbach Hinterglemm</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><strong>Up to two full day guided walks every week. </strong>   </p>
<p>Nestled amid sprawling hills and towering mountain ridges, the area is a haven for walkers. With over 400 kilometres of well-defined trails and 30 charming mountain huts to discover, it's perfect for walkers of all abilities.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102800/zellamsee_austria_adobestock_479225452.jpg" alt="Zell am See Guided Walks" data-udi="umb://media/78921f084af74799b0930d525c12afc7" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/2631ac5f3f824554a6f8c73491b2efae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2631ac5f3f824554a6f8c73491b2efae}" title="Zell am See">Zell am See</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><strong>A full day guided walk every Tuesday and Thursday.</strong></p>
<p>After an adventure in the mountains? This resort has around 400 kilometres of marked walking trails and routes that cater for all abilities, there’s so much to explore.</p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13107087/adobestock_241619822.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7df1de85ec2f4172961a8a01d79db4f9" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/f172dae360244d6b8c3d139aef4e83b5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f172dae360244d6b8c3d139aef4e83b5}" title="Neustift">Neustift</a></h4>
<p><strong>A full day guided walk every Tuesday and Thursday.</strong></p>
<p>The Stubai Valley offers 850 kilometres of diverse walking trails suitable for all abilities, ranging from leisurely strolls to challenging mountain adventures.</p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102802/adobestock_223615874.jpg" alt="Kitzbuhel guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/9776b98756a34c0a93a6d77ba835aac8" /></div>
<h4><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739}" title="Kitzbuhel">Kitzbühel </a></strong></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><strong>A full day guided walk every Monday and Thursday or Friday.</strong></p>
<p>The Kitzbühel region offers 1,000 kilometres of scenic walking trails for all skill levels, complete with picturesque views, opportunities for refreshing swims in Schwarzsee lake, and a vibrant town centre experience.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id="france" style="text-align: left;">France Guided Walks</h3>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-5">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13094410/chamonix-alps-summer.jpg?width=500&amp;height=238.52295409181636" alt="chamonix guided walks" /></div>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a></h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>A full day guided walk every Monday and Friday.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Discover the captivating charms of Chamonix. From relaxing strolls to challenging hikes, it’s the perfect outdoor playground. Lots of the walks are at a high altitude so in some areas you’ll still be able to see snow in the middle of summer.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-5">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13102803/morzine_adobestock_215697222.jpg" alt="Morzine guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/67d5ea7901a247b9a95161a6bc3e5eae" /></div>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc}" title="Morzine">Morzine</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>A full day guided walk every Monday and Friday. </strong>  </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Morzine has a variety of trails suitable for all, from serene walks at lower altitudes to challenging walks at higher elevations. Its beautiful natural scenery and stunning panoramic views offer an unforgettable experience.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h3 id="italy" style="text-align: left;">Italy Guided Walks</h3>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102804/adobestock_15756627.jpg" alt="Italy guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/58b016d6975041609f4b66a533a46689" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino">Bardolino</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><strong>A guided walk every Monday (full day) and Friday (half day).</strong></p>
<p><span>Here, you'll find diverse walking trails range from easy to challenging, spanning scenic vineyards, olive groves, historical sites, and Mediterranean Maquis with stunning views and ancient rock carvings.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102805/002_nicola_angeli_157_sassolungo.jpg" alt="Italy guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/b0a363b5e1be4b9fb3ac50ba16e5a228" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/7075240655bf40a19a9c77b24d8c5082" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7075240655bf40a19a9c77b24d8c5082}" title="Canazei">Canazei</a></h4>
<p><strong>A full day guided walk every Monday and Friday.</strong></p>
<p>Canazei, with its lush and varied landscape and extensive mountain trails, offers a wide range of walks for all abilities, making it a great choice for families looking to get the children outdoors.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102812/adobestock_609713524.jpg" alt="Garda guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/795c9b5143dd45e5b56ce9886a666805" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/689f022eb7974a7087ccbecf4adbda43" href="/{localLink:umb://document/689f022eb7974a7087ccbecf4adbda43}" title="Garda">Garda</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><strong>A guided walk every Monday (full day) and Friday (half day).</strong></p>
<p><span>Garda offers tranquil, flat lakeside walks and diverse trails on Monte Baldo with stunning views, along with unique attractions like Bronze Age rock carvings on Monte Luppia and the Sisan museum for bird and water life exploration.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102813/lake-iseo_adobestock_378117848-1.jpg" alt="Lake Iseo Guided Walks" data-udi="umb://media/1624a8b7620a415dae935753ff03f157" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9}" title="Lake Iseo">Lake Iseo</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<div class="flex-1 overflow-hidden">
<div class="react-scroll-to-bottom--css-wtlqh-79elbk h-full">
<div class="react-scroll-to-bottom--css-wtlqh-1n7m0yu">
