<div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light">
<p><strong>A guided walk every Tuesday (full day) and Friday (half day).</strong></p>
<p>Lake Iseo offers diverse walking experiences for all abilities, from exploring the natural pyramids of Zone and 'Giant Bench' installations to leisurely lakeside strolls and Franciacorta wine tasting opportunities.</p>
