</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102814/adobestock_564958767.jpg" alt="Lake Maggiore Guided Walks" data-udi="umb://media/4b4431e01bdd4766ae5fc05413b767b4" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48" href="/{localLink:umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48}" title="Lake Maggiore">Lake Maggiore</a></h4>
<p><strong>A guided walk every Tuesday (full day) and Friday (half day) in Stresa and Baveno  </strong></p>
<p><span>Lake Maggiore's guided walks, shared between Baveno and Stresa, range from relaxed floral promenades to adventurous mountain trails, featuring forested paths through villages and scenic lakeside marsh trails in Fondotoce Nature Reserve.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102815/limone.jpg" alt="Limone Guided Walks" data-udi="umb://media/a5ed7a85aecf490bb1f0b74d328a72f3" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c}" title="Limone">Limone</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><strong>A guided walk every Monday (full day) and Friday (half day).</strong></p>
<p><span>Limone is one of the best resorts for walking in <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a>. The gorgeous cobbled streets lead up to several great viewpoints, and you can see spectacular views of the lake from almost everywhere.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102816/merano-vineyards-1.jpg" alt="Merano guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/3ebbc681914e48969c2a7f2fdd3286e3" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7}" title="Merano">Merano</a></h4>
<p><strong>A full day guided walk every Monday and Friday.</strong></p>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><span>Merano boasts awe-inspiring vistas of the surrounding valleys and mountains, along with unspoiled natural beauty at your feet, making it an ideal destination for exploring the region's mountains and their surroundings.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102811/adobestock_223757480.jpg" alt="Montecatini guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/72afd0e6d6f742e5ad58c309def0d393" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/4cead924140a465fa8868775d321e171" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4cead924140a465fa8868775d321e171}" title="Montecatini" data-anchor="#">Montecatini</a></h4>
<p><strong>A full day guided walk every Monday and Friday.</strong></p>
<p><span>Montecatini Terme, known for its picturesque Tuscan countryside with Italian Cypress trees and rolling hills, is crossed by the well-signposted Camino di San Jacopo, offering unique wooded, hilly trails and ancient villages, a delight for walkers seeking varied landscapes.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102810/puez-odle-natural-parkpng.jpg" alt="selva guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/fddc11b8652d421f89825927b3ab2b17" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva">Selva</a></h4>
<p><strong>A full day guided walk every Monday and Friday.</strong></p>
<p><span>Selva has everything you need to make your trip unforgettable- unlimited walking trails, scenic 360-degree mountain vistas, and delectable local cuisine and wine. Regardless of your abilities, you'll find an outdoor activity that fits your needs.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id="madeira" style="text-align: left;">Madeira Guided Walks</h3>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><strong>A guided walk every Tuesday (full day) and Thursday (half day) in Funchal and Caniço. </strong></p>
<p>Experience the enchanting beauty of Madeira on foot. From leisurely strolls amidst lush orchards and prehistoric laurel forests, to exhilarating ascents towards majestic mountains and dramatic gorges, each trail promises a unique adventure. Please note: <span>the guided walks in Madeira are open to everyone and are not exclusive to Inghams guests.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-image">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102860/adobestock_62022455.jpg" alt="Madeira guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/f50413290da648ffae2573758804dc9e" /></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id="slovenia" style="text-align: left;">Slovenia Guided Walks</h3>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102861/adobestock_218855256.jpg" alt="slovenia guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/1abb237cdbe64545bec02a7e96b7d367" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><strong>A full day guided walk every Monday and Friday</strong></p>
<p><span>Explore the serene beauty of Lake Bohinj, a hidden gem in the heart of Triglav National Park. The forests around the lake offer a tranquil escape, with paths that are gentle and welcoming, perfect for all ages and abilities.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102862/slovenia-5.jpg" alt="Lake bled guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/8daade7e00fa49308720a19c5ee87ff9" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled</a></h4>
<p><strong>Join a full day guided walk every Monday and Friday from Lake Bohinj    </strong>  </p>
<p><span>At our Lake Bled resort, the guided walks primarily take place in the scenic Bohinj area, but guests staying in Bled are welcome and encouraged to join these guided walks every Monday and Friday from Lake Bohinj.</span></p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102874/adobestock_220959569-1.jpg" alt="kranjska gora guided walks" data-udi="umb://media/d654bead7aec42d7aa17c05952e5dd42" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a></h4>
<p><strong>A full day guided walk every Monday and Friday</strong></p>
<p>Take in the stunning views of the Julian Alps, breathe the crisp mountain air and explore the marked walking trails that offer a variety of options, from leisurely meadow walks to challenging hill hikes.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3 id="switzerland" style="text-align: left;">Switzerland Guided Walks</h3>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13102864/adobestock_523620686-1.jpg" alt="walking in zermatt" data-udi="umb://media/fdf71fa64a7b485fa3182db85e9e87c9" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><strong>A half day guided walk every Monday and Friday</strong></p>
<p><span>Zermatt’s jaw-dropping setting, surrounded by an impressive 38 peaks, including the world-renowned Matterhorn. Here, visitors can experience the very best walking trails, as well as an extensive network of lifts and mountain trains.</span></p>
