<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a></h4>
<p><strong>Two guided walks a week from a program of four walks with full and half-day options</strong></p>
<p><span>Located at the foot of the iconic Eiger Mountain, Grindelwald is one of the most picturesque locations in the Bernese Alps. It forms part of the Jungfrau region, which boasts hundreds of kilometres of trails.</span></p>
