<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3}" title="Wengen">Wengen</a></h4>
<p><strong><span>Two guided walks a week from a program of four walks with full and half-day options    </span></strong></p>
<p><span>Wengen offers dramatic scenery, with a sunny plateau beneath the Eiger, Mönch, and Jungfrau mountains providing spectacular views of the Lauterbrunnen Valley. You’ll have access to hundreds of kilometers of hiking through stunning mountain scenery.</span>.</p>
